FBIS3-48840 "dreas020_c_94002" FBIS-EAS-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 North Korea PRC on Patriot Missiles Deployment in ROK SK3101051894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0504 GMT 31 Jan 94 SK3101051894 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, January 31 (KCNA) -- A spokesman for the Foreign Ministry of China said that China does not approve of any actions detrimental to peace and stability on the Korean peninsula. The spokesman made the remark at a weekly press conference in Beijing on January 27 when asked to comment on a report that the United States is planning to deploy "Patriot" missiles in South Korea, XINHUA reported.
